{"tid":1441401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請抗爭者不用再顧慮民意，他們不是運動的stakeholder","createTime":"2019-08-10T15:56:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:32:06.000Z","uid":265443,"like":59,"dislike":101,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"9005a5f3bca10d8565a331a2c9429f69815aa135","tid":1441401,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:56:26.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇左cctvb無線個條例修訂節目<br />\n<br />\n其中訪問左一個金鐘餐廳嘅老闆，佢話自己<strong>612，616，805都照常營業</strong>，616送過水俾示威者，懶係企係反送中個邊咁<br />\n<br />\n其實講到尾佢最著緊嘅，都係自己餐廳嘅營業額<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個節目好明顯吹緊個風就係：你地繼續亂落去，本身支持你地嘅人都會討厭你地！<br />\n<br />\n所謂民意就係咁虛無嘅一樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話就話自己小市民，但係永遠高高在上，永遠得個up字，如果你影響到佢，兩秒佢就會改變立場<br />\n<br />\n唔好忘記，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">抗爭者都係普通小市民</span></strong>，你嘅意志priority要放最高，唔駛俾所謂民意影響行動<br />\n<br />\n你每對人溫柔，就係對自己殘忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為民意<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">并無實際作用</span></span>，普通市民一日無落場玩一日都係無任何影響力，盡快認清事實會比較好<br />\n<br />\n引導更多人起身反抗，無論立場正反，敲響非日常嘅鐘聲，持續社會亂局，先係可行方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁即係點？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>請大家鼓勵同支持各種新式及進取嘅行動方案</strong></span>，<strong>叫停任何野都係毒害，非常唔健康</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">個人認為非暴力嘅方案最易實行所以最可取</span><br />\n過份偏激行動盡量制止但是亦請理解，多理性討論，不割𥱊<br />\n<br />\n啱聽請幫推，唔啱聽請comment做良性討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef9ce8e7400d662c616c8c5444f6ad47fb163732","tid":1441401,"uid":265443,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:58:19.000Z","msg":"自推10下"},{"pid":"8f0eff79cf7206b247b0951cbb43f33d70aee8b5","tid":1441401,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:58:30.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"d8d068a45cc8d19f31408d88840e26fade681203","tid":1441401,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:58:40.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"8c6b17bdb92968c4dc027956daa335bdc426d098","tid":1441401,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:58:50.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"99af78bb4a8c8b41ce56b6ec905cd47daf6207b2","tid":1441401,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:59:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ccdd4fbf5f735574da6486d1c75e4b58594c9a71","tid":1441401,"uid":45684,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:59:09.000Z","msg":"并<br />\n<br />\n扣三毛"},{"pid":"d925452ff3c8e744c5a6b5283aeea75d133caae7","tid":1441401,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:59:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0b920e525f58f707c262d31c944c8125022c668","tid":1441401,"uid":265443,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"ccdd4fbf5f735574da6486d1c75e4b58594c9a71","tid":1441401,"uid":45684,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:59:09.000Z","msg":"并<br />\n<br />\n扣三毛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:59:49.000Z","msg":"說好的討論呢師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ab5cbb6d580f4f486d8133a3f630c50acdd4c1","tid":1441401,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:59:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"572d1ac6c01b4f4023d87f95529cf800421d09f3","tid":1441401,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:00:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d03f4ff1cbf90e89daa228067297bfd1512a863a","tid":1441401,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:00:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b9e109990670570bbdc4b1295e12967281109da","tid":1441401,"uid":193026,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:00:35.000Z","msg":"民意，係靠民宣去搵返來，唔係靠抗爭者<br />\n<br />\n呢部份交返俾和理非做吧"},{"pid":"a5eaef274e50d5ff3145d387386c857562dce568","tid":1441401,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:00:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d28c06ff35b3744c546e15aa96c079afcbbb9bfc","tid":1441401,"uid":286918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:01:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R7Kxwac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR7Kxwac.jpg&h=ed285c89&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fQ2Gpvc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfQ2Gpvc.jpg&h=d948a2db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"658c7cb29213dbbcec015b0bfbee920f8d8448f0","tid":1441401,"uid":265904,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:02:22.000Z","msg":"歷史上有咩抗爭運動係可以唔洗顧慮民意而成功?"},{"pid":"76586a396b9486a50b9e3e3093932fb161afb017","tid":1441401,"uid":265443,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9b9e109990670570bbdc4b1295e12967281109da","tid":1441401,"uid":193026,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:00:35.000Z","msg":"民意，係靠民宣去搵返來，唔係靠抗爭者<br />\n<br />\n呢部份交返俾和理非做吧"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:02:33.000Z","msg":"認同，諗民意交俾和理非，<br />\n行動派只要落實執行就得"},{"pid":"8f238e77199ec0bc641871d217fa7d1702264508","tid":1441401,"uid":35699,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:03:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">并</span></span><br />\n<br />\n三毛確認"},{"pid":"ef05bea7177c07bc0952d083c0c6a70ad2d74f0b","tid":1441401,"uid":41901,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9b9e109990670570bbdc4b1295e12967281109da","tid":1441401,"uid":193026,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:00:35.000Z","msg":"民意，係靠民宣去搵返來，唔係靠抗爭者<br />\n<br />\n呢部份交返俾和理非做吧"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:03:39.000Z","msg":"on9 剩係得文宣先搵到民意?<br />\n唔係警察亂射TG扑市民, 把火會吹得咁行?"},{"pid":"3236aecd0550d9